title: ‘Succession’ Season 3 Episode 5, With J. Smith-Cameron
description:
Sean and Joanna are back to talk about the latest episode of 'Succession,' "Retired Janitors of Idaho." They discuss the fallout of the shareholder meeting and the deal that is made to keep the Roys in power. Later, Joanna is joined by actor J. Smith-Cameron to talk about Gerri's ride this season and what is going on in her head (55:43).
Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Joanna Robinson
Guest: J. Smith-Cameron
Producer: Steve Ahlman
